Ctrl + u – clear the terminal prompt
Ctrl + l – clear the terminal contents
Ctrl + r – search the history
Ctrl + a – move the cursor to the beginning of the prompt
Ctrl + e – move the cursor to the end of the prompt
Ctrl + k – deletes the characters from the cursor to the end of the line
Ctrl + w – deletes the word before the cursor
F11      – insert `~` character